trans-unit.source: Collects exceptions that occurred during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: Raccoglie le eccezioni generate durante l'individuazione dei servizi Web XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe non può essere ereditata.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Errors%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Errors%2A> proprietà di <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> è di tipo <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL that caused an exception during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: URL che ha generato un'eccezione durante l'individuazione di servizi Web XML.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> that occurred during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> generato durante l'individuazione di servizi Web XML.

trans-unit.source: Adds an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with a key of <paramref name="url" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Aggiunge un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> con una chiave di <paramref name="url" /> a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> è <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An entry with a key of <paramref name="url" /> already exists in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Esiste già una voce con una chiave di <paramref name="url" /> in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> to locate within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: URL dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> da individuare all'interno di <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contains an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with the specified URL.
trans-unit.target: Determina se <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contiene un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> con l'URL specificato.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contains an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with the specified URL; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contiene un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> con l'URL specificato; in caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> è <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the discovery document that caused an exception to be thrown during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: URL del documento di individuazione che ha generato un'eccezione durante l'individuazione di servizi Web XML.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> that occurred while discovering the specified URL from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene o imposta l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> generato durante l'individuazione dell'URL specificato dall'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> that was thrown discovering <paramref name="url" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> generato durante l'individuazione di <paramref name="url" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> è <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> object with all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> con tutte le chiavi presenti in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the keys of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> contenente le chiavi dell'interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: URL dell'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> da rimuovere da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with the specified URL from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Rimuove un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> con l'URL specificato da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> è <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> object containing all the values in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> contenente tutti i valori presenti in <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the values in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> contenente i valori dell'interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
